title: Anna
overview: It all started with a little lie. Yu Mi is living a different life now. At some point, she began to believe in her lies and lost a part of herself. As a result, only Ji Hong's ambitious husband and Ji Won are left with her, the only friend Yoo Mi can trust. Hyun Joo is a woman who lives her life putting herself above everyone, not treating them with kindness or malice. She has a slightly strained relationship with Yu Mi.
